movies.title: Kanymda Kumiss
movies.shortDescription:
They say the biking is just a pretext. An excuse to open doors and open minds. Following Fred Horny from Bishkek to the Lenin Peak, Kanymda kumiss is more than a mountain bike movie. It's an adventure. Descending rapid rivers in his packraft, sharing times with nomads while the 30th anniversary of the country's independance, follow the rider to reach the final exceptional rides, starting at an altitude of 5500M.

Directed by
Jrmie Reuiller
